Application.Domain

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Domain.Credentials
      • Application.Domain.User

  • @Entity
public class User
extends Credentials
    User is the class that maps the database Entity User. A User contains all the useful information about the citizens who use the platform.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corti Lorenzo, Tocchetti Andrea
